For example, here:
```
MainGUI mainGUI = new MainGUI(player);
NameGUI nameGUI = new NameGUI(player);
SkinGUI skinGUI = new SkinGUI(player);
```
You are creating 3 GUIs, so 3 new inventory click event register in listener.

